text: Cosmic Voyage () is a 1936 Soviet silent science fiction movie directed by Vasili Zhuravlyov.Космический рейсБолее 70 редких фильмов из архивов Госфильмофонда появились на портале "Культура.РФ" It stars Sergei Komarov, Ksenia Moskalenko, and Vassili Gaponenko. == Actors == * Sergei Komarov as Pavel Ivanovich Sedikh * Ksenia Moskalenko as Marina, Karin's assistant * Vassili Gaponenko as Andryusha Orlov * Nikolai Feoktistov as Capt.
